702424f-b.title: Brooklyn: 5th Street (South) - Marcy Avenue
702424f-b.text:
South 5th Street, east from Marcy Avenue. At the corner (right)
is a synagogue and in the background is St. Pauks Evangelical
Lgtheran Chursh.
View 2 shows a parking space just west of 'Tarcy -venue.
P. L. Sperr  September lu, 1941
